model_specification: U = b + split_self - gamma * max((combined_earning * (token_self / (token_self + token_opp)) - split_self), 0)
model_summary: A utility model for responder behavior that computes the acceptance utility by comparing the offered monetary share to a fairness expectation derived from the ratio of self tokens to total tokens. A baseline parameter and an inequity sensitivity parameter penalize offers that fall below this fair share.
